pageContext.claim: “Congressman Sean Duffy. We miss him. But he signed with CNN. They paid him a lot of money, and they don't put them on. Why? Because I’m pro-Trump. You think that’s fair, right? He’s pro-Trump. So what they've done is paid him money to silence him because he has a very important voice.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump habitually criticizes CNN with ridiculous, false claims. Duffy continues to appear on CNN, even as he has garnered criticism for anti-immigrant remarks and for spreading a debunked conspiracy theory that Ukraine and not Russia interfered in the 2016 U.S. election.
